## Common Pitfalls
- Calendar year ≠ Fiscal year — this is the #1 source of errors
- Values may be revised in later bulletins — use the bulletin issue specified
- Surplus values may be positive while deficit values are negative (check table conventions)
- Some tables use parentheses for negative numbers
- Column headers often span multiple lines — read the full header

